## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="1d95c-104">根據預設，WMI 方法名稱會是目標方法的名稱。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1d95c-104">By default, the WMI method name will be the name of the target method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="1d95c-105">這個屬性的父類別<xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementMemberAttribute>，包含名稱的參數。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1d95c-105">The parent class of this attribute, <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementMemberAttribute>, includes a Name parameter.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="1d95c-106">若要變更的方法，透過 WMI 公開，而不需要變更您的內部方法名稱的名稱，您可以使用該參數。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1d95c-106">You can use that parameter to change the name of the method that is exposed through WMI without changing your internal method name.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="1d95c-107">必須是公用的方法，並不是靜態。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1d95c-107">The method must be public and it may be static.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="1d95c-108">它可以包含任意組合的 [in]、 [out] [in/out]，陣列或物件參考參數。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1d95c-108">It can include any combination of [in], [out], [in/out], array or object reference parameters.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="1d95c-109">由於 WMI 所加諸的限制不得多維度或不規則陣列參數。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1d95c-109">Array parameters cannot be multidimensional or jagged because of limitations imposed by WMI.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="1d95c-110">可以是方法的傳回型別： void、 純量、 字串、 日期時間或物件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1d95c-110">The return type of the method can be: void, scalar, string, datetime or object.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="1d95c-111">它不能是陣列。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1d95c-111">It cannot be an array.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="1d95c-112">下列範例顯示如何將方法標示為含有 ManagementTask 屬性公開至 WMI 方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1d95c-112">The following example shows how to mark a method with the ManagementTask attribute to expose the method to WMI.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="1d95c-113">方法會顯示在 WMI 中為 ResetCounters。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1d95c-113">The method will show up in WMI as ResetCounters.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
// Use the ManagementTask attribute to specify that a method  
// is exposed to WMI through this provider. Consumers will be  
// able to execute this method through WMI.  
[ManagementTask]  
public void ResetCounters()  
{  
    counter.Reset();  
}  
```
